{"tid":2129480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維基百科已經有記載「慶回歸群組」和「富臨群組」","createTime":"2020-07-28T15:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T10:06:34.000Z","uid":71237,"like":80,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac0f6037f19f5728efae1ce2b16b5d8ebb32de2","tid":2129480,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:17:21.000Z","msg":"慶回歸群組<br />\n<a href=\"https://w.wiki/X$a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.wiki%2FX%24a&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=5fb37e81\" target=\"_blank\">https://w.wiki/X$a</a><br />\n<br />\n富臨群組<br />\n<a href=\"https://w.wiki/Y8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.wiki%2FY8A&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=d65636fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://w.wiki/Y8A</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794ef41a8f4b9aa2bb0b6dd1e1f22d37b1f60ff9","tid":2129480,"uid":71237,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"如果你都想喺維基百科寫嘢，喺寫之前不妨睇下我們提供的新手教學。<br />\n因為維基百科的特徵就係任何人都可以修改，好多人擔心自己寫嘅嘢會俾五毛亂刪。<br />\n但其實只要你花半個鐘時間去了解咗基本規則，你就會知道點樣寫先唔會輕易被刪除。<br />\n（相反如果你唔了解基本規則，你寫嘅嘢太差勁，就算我係同路人都會想刪除你寫嘅嘢。）<br />\n<br />\n目前維基百科活躍寫反送中運動嘅香港人大概只有十幾個，人手真係嚴重不足。<br />\n我們需要更多新血加入，多你一個就真係好多。好多嘢你唔寫就真係永遠無人寫。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係新手，可以閱讀以下的新手教學：<br />\n維基百科戰線招募長期參與者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1</a><br />\n[教學] 如何成為維基百科撰寫師？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你喺維基百科遇到問題，可以入telegram group搵其他資深維基人協助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/KFecO0enbau0gmUBnvZEtQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKFecO0enbau0gmUBnvZEtQ&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=f1c4319b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/KFecO0enbau0gmUBnvZEtQ</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你想幫手寫嘢/做資料搜集，可以入telegram channel，睇下有咩條目需要幫手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkwikichannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkwikichannel&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=8b01514d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkwikichannel</a><br />\n<br />\n如果大家發現維基百科有嘢值得寫/有惡意破壞，可以用維基百科(Wikipedia)報料Bot向我地報告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wikiscout_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwikiscout_bot&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=96bd1acd\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wikiscout_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你想了解關於維基百科戰線的最新消息，可以like我地的Facebook page。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%B6%AD%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A-103027814743750/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%2599%25BE%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%25B7%259A-103027814743750%2F&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=82fff4f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%B6%AD%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A-103027814743750/</a><br />\n<br />\n我們亦都有網站提供教學文章、實用工具。<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/hkwikiteam/index\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Fhkwikiteam%2Findex&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=450e2cfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/hkwikiteam/index</a>"},{"pid":"0c4e0daae1dafed5b94750e7bf41bd430ce122dd","tid":2129480,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"Econ巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"